      <memberdef kind="define" id="group__led__interface_1ga537f733ae3070fbe279834c76cda35ae" prot="public" static="no">
        <name>LED_DT_SPEC_GET</name>
        <param><defname>node_id</defname></param>
        <initializer>	{                                                                      \
		.dev = <ref refid="group__device__model_1ga9a65996ce21f43acb7db061e23b48ec7" kindref="member">DEVICE_DT_GET</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1ga3ac56d491510275ee1321446796ab63b" kindref="member">DT_PARENT</ref>(node_id)),                      \
		.index = <ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1ga34452788d4fed1fce3e6650d61246866" kindref="member">DT_NODE_CHILD_IDX</ref>(node_id),                           \
	}</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Static initializer for a struct <ref refid="structled__dt__spec" kindref="compound">led_dt_spec</ref>. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This returns a static initializer for a struct <ref refid="structled__dt__spec" kindref="compound">led_dt_spec</ref> given a devicetree node identifier.</para>
<para>Example devicetree fragment:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">leds<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>compatible<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;gpio-leds&quot;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>led0:<sp/>led_0<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>...</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Example usage:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".c"><codeline><highlight class="keyword">const</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">struct<sp/></highlight><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structled__dt__spec" kindref="compound">led_dt_spec</ref><sp/>spec<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="group__led__interface_1ga537f733ae3070fbe279834c76cda35ae" kindref="member">LED_DT_SPEC_GET</ref>(<ref refid="group__devicetree-generic-id_1gab7d23294a6bf7fd44a98b48ec47d8a79" kindref="member">DT_NODELABEL</ref>(led0));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Initializes<sp/>&apos;spec&apos;<sp/>to:</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>{</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.dev<sp/>=<sp/>DEVICE_DT_GET(DT_PARENT(led0)),</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>.index<sp/>=<sp/>0,</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The device (dev) must still be checked for readiness, e.g. using <ref refid="group__device__model_1gaa4944bd850e90cbd52b0489f9b12edfb" kindref="member">device_is_ready()</ref>.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>node_id</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Devicetree node identifier.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Static initializer for a struct <ref refid="structled__dt__spec" kindref="compound">led_dt_spec</ref> for the property. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
